      h1 Learn to row
      p Sunderland Rowing Club runs a learn to row courses during the year. The courses typically consist of 8 sessions of 2 hours where our volunteer coaches will take you through the basics of rowing technique. When you complete the course, you will then be able to decide whether to take up the sport competitively and join one of the training squads or you might decide to concentrate on the more sociable aspects of rowing
      br
      a.link-button(href='/members/learn') Learn more
    
